strings: <voice_0x01001CDB><se_high>Media princess: Sorry, I don't want to see you cry.
<voice_0x01001CDC><se_high>Media princess: I just couldn't get Martha out of my mind. Amazing auntie...
<voice_0x01001CDD><se_high>Media princess: But you have to try not to think about it. We're going to spend some time together... and talk about good things.
<voice_0x01001CDE><se_high>Media princess: For the first time in my life, I saw snow. Beautiful like a big, fluffy white rug...
<voice_0x01001CDF><se_high>Media princess: You can not find it even if you play hide and seek! I am white as a horse
<voice_0x01001CE0><se_high>Media princess: Don't forget to love me when my time is up with you <hero>...
